data.description: Exquisite home! Swim/tennis community. Meticulously maintained.   Open & Airy. Shows like a model home with upgrades and addition along the way. Lots of windows through out. Sort after master on the main floor. 1st floor features: Sweeping 2 story foyer with view of catwalk. Great room with vaulted ceiling, fireplace & access to enclosed sunroom. Sunroom over looking a huge fenced back yard. Generous dining room with bay window. Cozy keeping room off the  kitchen w/ bay window over looking the back yard. Big beautiful kitchen w/ granite-c tops, stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinets & walk in pantry. Ample breakfast area w/ bay window open to kitchen and keeping room.   Upper level features: Tranquil master bedroom with lots of room for lounging, vaulted ceiling, palladian window & 2 large closets. Enormous master bath, w/ jetted tub, double vanities & private water closet. 2 master size bed room w/ unbelievable closet space. 4th large bedroom w/ roomy closet. Tremendous space in this home. Great access to the freeway, plenty of near by shopping & you must checkout nearby International park.
